{"talk":{"id":39981,"name":"Elizabeth Dunn: Helping others makes us happier -- but it matters how we do it","description":"Research shows that helping others makes us happier. But in her groundbreaking work on generosity and joy, social psychologist Elizabeth Dunn found that there's a catch: it matters how we help. Learn how we can make a greater impact -- and boost our own happiness along the way -- if we make one key shift in how we help others. \"Let's stop thinking about giving as just this moral obligation and start thinking of it as a source of pleasure,\" Dunn says.","slug":"elizabeth_dunn_helping_others_makes_us_happier_but_it_matters_how_we_do_it","recorded_at":"2019-04-15 00:00:00","published_at":"2019-04-26 11:12:18","updated_at":"2021-04-13 21:27:23","viewed_count":0,"emailed_count":0,"event":{"id":597,"name":"TED2019"},"images":[{"image":{"size":"113x85","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/64737c0dcacc2fe76b6f4c643e480eb7cbf22d0a_113x85.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"240x180","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/64737c0dcacc2fe76b6f4c643e480eb7cbf22d0a_240x180.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"615x461","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/64737c0dcacc2fe76b6f4c643e480eb7cbf22d0a_615x461.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"2400x1800","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/64737c0dcacc2fe76b6f4c643e480eb7cbf22d0a_2400x1800.jpg"}}],"image_16x9":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/44d50ca04e879fc1fa8645e00e0ff8cb3d5120c9_2880x1620.jpg","media":{"internal":{"64k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/ElizabethDunn_2019-64k.mp4?apikey=c692baa7dafbf74e4fbde1ac88b44cafc96cfe7a","filesize_bytes":7177278,"mime_type":"video\/mp4"},"180k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/ElizabethDunn_2019-180k.mp4?apikey=c692baa7dafbf74e4fbde1ac88b44cafc96cfe7a","filesize_bytes":19863051,"mime_type":"video\/mp4"},"320k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/ElizabethDunn_2019-320k.mp4?apikey=c692baa7dafbf74e4fbde1ac88b44cafc96cfe7a","filesize_bytes":351